parameters:
Welcome to Hatayaki Village!... That's what it says. Since
there are no tourists, no one will read it.

Here are the delightful pigs! Let's touch them and become
happy with their warmth!

I am growing corn for pig farming. Theft is a crime. You
should never do it. Don't you think it's pitiful to see cute
pigs go hungry?

It's as if... it resembles Lunaroa's flames... My health has
fully recovered!

\SE[2]The weak ones who couldn't choose are pitiful, aren't
they? \SE[0]But even the strong ones who can choose have
their own difficulties. \SE[0]...right? \SE[0]What do you
think, Laura?

\SE[16]But you also understood about Mom, right? \SE[0]We've
taken a step closer to mutual understanding, haven't we?

\SE[65]Is it okay for me to see something like this on my
own...? \SE[60]Lunaroa probably doesn't want to be known
either...

\SE\SE[4]I don't really understand, but... \!\SE[3]Isn't it
harder to bear it alone without anyone knowing? \!\SE[4]If
it were me, I wouldn't want that.

\SE[2]Maybe Mom thought it would be fine if it was you, so
she asked you to come alone.
